{"tid":1008346,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"彭博公布華為另一案  FBI調查華為竊取初創鑽石螢幕設計","createTime":"2019-02-04T12:00:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-05T05:03:13.000Z","uid":141151,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"c189222d2fdb419a3f73e9e11459bfe6e6847798","tid":1008346,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T12:00:00.000Z","msg":"Huawei Sting Offers Rare Glimpse of the U.S. Targeting a Chinese Giant<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2019-02-04/huawei-sting-offers-rare-glimpse-of-u-s-targeting-chinese-giant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Ffeatures%2F2019-02-04%2Fhuawei-sting-offers-rare-glimpse-of-u-s-targeting-chinese-giant&d=KChxWXaIVet3ZRtCu1MdJxnwB9%2FpnwrfV4lJUXhph6I%3D&h=cd9d7ee6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2019-02-04/huawei-sting-offers-rare-glimpse-of-u-s-targeting-chinese-giant</a>"},{"pid":"c814904d9129a20ab963deb2b1b78ef859d317ff","tid":1008346,"uid":28307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T12:02:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73de1a3d5ad99e35644c9c822bd04249c049a9ef","tid":1008346,"uid":48083,"like":33,"dislike":1,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T13:20:34.000Z","msg":"1. 鑽石mon老板同華為（潛在客戶）傾好，俾sample華為睇，跟行規講明唔準破壞sample以免re-engineering<br />\n<br />\n⋯⋯By February 2017, the two companies had a deal. Akhan would ship two samples of Miraj to Huawei in San Diego. According to a letter of intent, signed by both parties, Huawei promised to return any samples within 60 days and also to limit any tests it might perform to methods that wouldn&rsquo;t cause damage. (The latter provision is standard in the industry and is designed to make it hard to reverse-engineer any intellectual property.)⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2. 結果華為遲交回sample<br />\n原本兩個月，結果搞咗約7個月<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nThe first sign of trouble came two months later, in May, when Huawei missed the deadline to return the sample. Shurboff says his emails to Han requesting its immediate return were ignored. <br />\n<br />\nThe following month, Han wrote that Huawei had been performing &ldquo;standard&rdquo; tests on the sample and included a photo showing a big scratch on its surface. Finally, a package from Huawei showed up at Gurnee on Aug. 2.  <br />\n<br />\n3. 一開箱，sample散撚哂<br />\n仲有部分鑽石層唔見咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nShurboff⋯ could tell something was wrong when he picked up the case. It rattled. The unscratchable Miraj sample wasn&rsquo;t just scratched; it was broken in two, and three shards of diamond glass were missing.<br />\n<br />\nShurboff says he knew there was no way the sample could have been damaged in shipping&mdash;all the pieces would still be there in the case. Instead, he believed that Huawei had tried to cut through the sample to gauge the thickness of its diamond film and to figure out how Akhan had engineered it. &ldquo;My heart sank,&rdquo; he says. &ldquo;I thought, &lsquo;Great, this multibillion-dollar company is coming after our technology. What are we going to do now?&rsquo;&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n4. FBI調查，估計華為用100KW 激光射爆佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n⋯⋯They recall the gemologist saying he&rsquo;d analyzed the diamond glass sample and concluded that Huawei had blasted it with a 100-kilowatt laser, powerful enough to be used as a weapon.<br />\n<br />\n5. 今年1月28日，fbi突擊搜查華為<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nOn the same day Wray&rsquo;s statement was released, the government searched the Huawei lab in San Diego where Akhan&rsquo;s glass had been sent<br />\n<br />\n待續⋯⋯"},{"pid":"c9f1af880b268aca4d2fae38c633226a9e3d6675","tid":1008346,"uid":44105,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T13:32:16.000Z","msg":"睇怕得番中国自己玩"},{"pid":"8644727c4431f04b8b7ca802640aef8a3ff4ca7f","tid":1008346,"uid":62646,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T13:50:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5f3edb79d4c03765f375ecc3a8f90a05204a60e","tid":1008346,"uid":123082,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T13:57:15.000Z","msg":"咁都信華為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw有條屍比返佢已經好比面<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e487c63cb29b7ea3cedbca51e7c24d7c0be32e3e","tid":1008346,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T14:09:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4414b47f0322e82efccedbc8889c4a7cee2b973","tid":1008346,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T14:11:55.000Z","msg":"FBI忙到死了"},{"pid":"854b49728399eaa4005ed0e5c75fb97158e99d9e","tid":1008346,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f4414b47f0322e82efccedbc8889c4a7cee2b973","tid":1008346,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T14:11:55.000Z","msg":"FBI忙到死了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T14:14:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"280bab29ffd30a8fe1e5d27